Very cool Lolthorn, very cool.

Being a cleric myself, and reguarly fighting with two Paladins, I have experienced first hand the heal/hate/pound and then LoH on me from a pally before. 
Two fine Paladins, Wistful and Ripped have saved my butt on more than a few occasions, and I have even seen them LoH on each other.  (Sometimes I think it&#39;s a contest between the two to see who can hold out the longest...LOL.)  
I&#39;ve even been privy to a double LoH treatment at the same time from the two, and also laughed my ass off when it was too late and they either LoH on my corpse or the mob itself.....ROFL. 
 
Maybe I am spoiled...but I&#39;ve come to need a paladin in my group, and I will rarely travel without one.  I keep him alive, he keeps me alive, it&#39;s a win/win situation.  

I am honored and humbled by any paladin who would use LoH on their healer or whomever they deemed it necessary before letting them die and saving themselves first.  

Nice post Lolthorn.[/quote]

